quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  2,283,Vi vojagx ne scribe est available obligaci posxt garanti repayment! Unu fid en this manier li return obligaci when due li observ DI his Lord Ne withhold any testimony per concealing ki vi witnessed Anyone withholds testimony est sinful je kor DI EST fully aware da CXIO VI do
  2,284,Al DI aparten cxio heavens ter! Whether vi deklar your innermost thoughts keep them fel DI ten vi responsible por them. Li forgives whomever Li vol pun whomever Li vol! DI est Omnipotent
