  2,286,DI NENIAM SXARGX ANIM its means its KREDIT est KI gxi earns KONTRAUX est KI GXI commits Our Lord ne kondamn us ni forges far mistakes Our Lord protekt us el blaspheming Vi like those antaux us done Our Lord protekt us el pek gxi igx tro late us pent! Pardon us forgive us! Vi est our Lord Mastr Grant us victory disbelieving popol
