  3,7,Li send vi this scripture containing straightforward vers - which constitute esenc scripture - Ankaux as multiple-meaning allegorical vers. Those haven dub their kor pursue multiple-meaning vers kre confusion extricate nepr meaning Neniom kon prav meaning thereof escept DI those put founded knowledge! Ili dir Ni kred en this - all da gxi ven our Lord Nur those posed intelligence pren heed
